description = "rustyboi is a cycle-accurate Game Boy / Game Boy Color emulator written in Rust. This libretro core provides video, audio, joypad input, runtime-serialized save states, and a selectable hardware model (Auto/CGB/DMG). Note: in-cartridge battery (SRAM) saves are not yet persisted by this core — use save states."
